Fabrice Luchini https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fabrice_Luchini 0 Fabrice Luchini (French pronunciation: ​[fabʁis lykini]; born Robert Luchini; 1 November 1951) is a French stage and film actor. He has appeared in films such as Potiche, The Women on the 6th Floor, and In the House. For his role in the 2015 film Courted he won the Volpi Cup for Best Actor at the 72nd Venice International Film Festival.
